    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super reliable for all my daily errands and weekend getaways. It\u2019s been well-loved and looked after, so you\u2019re getting a car that\u2019s ready to hit the road right away! Perfect for anyone looking for a dependable vehicle without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
